  <brief_title>Tolerability of MK0524A Versus Niacin Extended-Release (0524A-054)</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Worldwide, Multicenter, Double-Blind, Parallel Study to Evaluate the Tolerability of MK0524A Versus Niacin Extended-Release</official_title>
  <sponsors>
    <lead_sponsor>
      <agency>Merck Sharp &amp; Dohme Corp.</agency>
