    </lead_sponsor>
  </sponsors>
  <source>Merck Sharp &amp; Dohme Corp.</source>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This is a 16-week clinical trial in lipid clinic patients for whom niacin therapy is
      appropriate to evaluate the tolerability of MK0524A versus niacin extended-release. There
      will be 6 scheduled clinic visits and 2 treatment groups.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
